text: Pascal Dubosquelle (born 2 January 1963) is a French rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:French male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
